snippet.title: Communite Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Communite is a multiplayer town building simulator!

Create your own village in a shared world, while helping others construct theirs!

Unlock new buildings, achieve community goals and gain rewards - all while co-operating with others and building a kind and adorable world.
